","tag-virtue-al-fadail","tag-warning-al-nudhr","tag-worldly-hopes-al-aml","tag-worldly-life-dunya"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9rB","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/20\/salah-ummah-zuhd\/","url_meta":{"origin":36307,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Righteousness in temperance, destruction in worldly hope","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe rightness in the beginning of this nation was by renouncing the world and attaining conviction. The destruction in the end of it is by miserliness and vain hopes.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad ibn H\u0323anbal 52\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/30\/disease-of-nations\/","url_meta":{"origin":36307,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: The Prophet warns against diseases of nations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the diseases of nations will afflict my nation.\" They said, \"O Messenger of Allah, what are the diseases of nations?\" The Prophet said, \"Insolence, hubris, turning their backs to one another, competing for worldly possessions,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40092,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/13\/give-up-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":36307,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Zuhd: Give up worldly life for Allah\u2019s love","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRenounce the worldly life and Allah will love you. As for people, leave this to them and they will love you.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 8\/41 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26070,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/14\/do-not-hope-hiyat-al-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":36307,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Do not place your hopes in worldly life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not be preoccupied with accumulating much wealth, such that you place your hope in the world.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2328 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23470,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/12\/prophet-fear-compete-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":36307,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Greed: The Prophet fears Muslims compete for wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI do not fear poverty for you, rather I fear that you will compete for riches. I do not fear for your mistakes, rather I fear for what you do on purpose.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 10958\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37793,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/05\/08\/traveler-provision\/","url_meta":{"origin":36307,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Zuhd: Enough of the world on journey to Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Khabbab ibn al-Aratt reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, it is enough for you to have in the world the likes of a traveler\u2019s provision.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 9916 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u06